{"tid":1630240,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[注意]係咪已經唔記得以武制暴嘅準則？","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:56:52.000Z","uid":257147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4803d8cdc720531a7b0b3c5aa7e78ec35e0f953c","tid":1630240,"uid":257147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:51:13.000Z","msg":"首先唔好再講私了。<br />\n<br />\n其次就係，馬x露 並沒有對現場手足做成致命傷害。影大頭，需要用另外方法解決。<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得黑面包青天？烏蠅貼變頹頭？<br />\n我相信呢種方法個效果所做成嘅心理傷害會更大<br />\n<br />\n雖然見到佢仆直我好撚心涼，但係會對文宣手足加重負荷。<br />\n<br />\n以武制暴係出現喺會有生命危險，同已對手足做成傷害下先應該出現。<br />\n<br />\n唔割，但係應該要進步並且用得其所。"},{"pid":"eeea5cb491ad914e8f24a1d7f041d1ad3871fd17","tid":1630240,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac280ff166acf921d0aec35e5e21e645edd7aa8f","tid":1630240,"uid":146286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"743cbc3158aaeb262be38cc857a9c8b70be7cfbb","tid":1630240,"uid":143827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"16d0eb3ac7cedfe27e4e8c971f6ac66959320769","tid":1630240,"uid":257147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:01:39.000Z","msg":"剃頭<br />\n黑面"},{"pid":"8b037b40205257e94766f6b8be07fe43925005af","tid":1630240,"uid":257147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"推下"}]}